# Battle Stage 1B - Setup Options Contract

This patch adds a read-only backend contract for the future mobile Battle modal.

## Endpoint

`GET /streams/:id/battles/setup-options`

Requires JWT auth.

## Purpose

The endpoint gives mobile the battle setup rules without allowing local-only battle starts.

It returns:

- stream and host eligibility
- supported battle types
- direct invite timer options
- random queue fixed duration
- team invite rules
- sudden death rules
- unresolved product decisions

## Important limits

This does not create generalized battle rows yet.

This does not run Prisma.

This does not apply migrations.

This does not expose the mobile Battle button yet.
